reviewText: The DVDs are great it's just an adrenaline rush of awesome the whole time your watching. Shipping was great on them too.
Travis and his crew will always amaze you or make you laugh your ass off. Yes there are some bad wrecks from time to time ,but anyone into motor sports isn't into it because its safe.

these guys are Awesome, the stunts they do are unbelievable... if I was half as good as these guys I would be wrapped.
Must buy DVD set, if you haven't got any of there stuff and are serious about  crazy moto x stunts
